- **Social media links** (@thegifbeat, @gifbeat.com)
- **Brand colors** (yellow, black, white, grey)
- **Mobile responsive** design
- **SEO optimized** with proper meta tags

## 📁 Project Structure

```
gifbeat-waitlist/
├── src/app/page.tsx          # Main landing page (all-in-one)
├── src/app/layout.tsx        # App layout with SEO
├── src/app/globals.css       # Styling and animations
├── src/lib/supabase/         # Database client
├── public/gifs/              # All your GIF assets
├── package.json              # Dependencies
├── README.md                 # Full documentation
├── DEPLOYMENT.md             # Detailed deployment guide
└── vercel.json               # Vercel configuration
```

## 🔧 Customization

**Change Colors**: Edit `/src/app/globals.css`  
**Update Copy**: Edit `/src/app/page.tsx`  
**Replace GIFs**: Add new GIFs to `/public/gifs/`  
**Social Links**: Update Instagram/TikTok handles in page.tsx  

## 📊 After Deployment

1. **Test the form** - Enter your email to verify it works
2. **Check Supabase** - View signups in Table Editor
3. **Share your URL** - Start collecting emails!
4. **Monitor growth** - Export emails as CSV when needed

## 🆘 Need Help?

- **Deployment issues**: Check `DEPLOYMENT.md` for troubleshooting
- **Code questions**: All code is well-commented in `page.tsx`
- **Design changes**: Everything is in one file for easy editing

